---
description: Database conventions and schema guidance
globs: src/db/**
alwaysApply: false
---
- All tables are defined in src/db/schema.ts using Drizzle's pgSchema().
- Do NOT modify the schema file directly. Schema changes must go through the central team.
- When querying, always import from src/db/schema.ts and use the Drizzle query builder.
- Use uuid for all primary keys.
- Include createdAt and updatedAt timestamps on all tables.
- Reference @src/db/schema.ts for the current table definitions.
